title: New: Kailee Morgue – Discovery
body:
Viral star **Kailee Morgue** released one of last years most buzz worth debut singles, in the form of the pop hit in waiting, _Medusa_.

Towards the tail end of 2017 she followed it up with another equally radio ready number, _Discovery_. Part Lorde, part BANKS, Morgue has all the makings of a star, and there’s no doubt that this year is set to be an impressive one for her. Check out Discovery below.
